---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'; 
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service | 2 Smokin' Barrels">
    <main>
        <div class="container" style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left; padding: 2rem; background: var(--bg-dark); border-radius: 10px;">
            <p style="color: var(--grey-med);"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> May 10, 2026</p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-red); margin-top: 2rem;">1. Acceptance of Terms</h3>
            <p>By accessing 2smokinbarrels.com and utilizing the Command Center, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use the interactive features of this site.</p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-red); margin-top: 2rem;">2. Description of Service</h3>
            <p>2 Smokin' Barrels provides interactive web tools ("Command Center") that allow viewers to trigger actions, overlays, and events on a live broadcast via a secure WebSocket connection to Streamer.bot.</p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-red); margin-top: 2rem;">3. User Conduct</h3>
            <p>You agree to use the Command Center responsibly. You shall not:</p>
            <ul style="color: var(--white-med); padding-left: 20px; line-height: 1.6;">
                <li>Use automated scripts, bots, or auto-clickers to spam the Command Center.</li>
                <li>Attempt to reverse-engineer, exploit, or bypass the point costs associated with stream actions.</li>
                <li>Use the service to transmit malicious code, payloads, or unauthorized WebSocket requests.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-red); margin-top: 2rem;">4. Account Access and Termination</h3>
            <p>Access to the Command Center is a privilege provided to the 2 Smokin' Barrels community. We reserve the right to ban, block, or revoke any user's access to the Command Center or the underlying stream database at our sole discretion, without notice, for abusive behavior or violation of these terms.</p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-red); margin-top: 2rem;">5. Limitation of Liability</h3>
            <p>The tools and services on this website are provided "as is" and "as available." 2 Smokin' Barrels makes no warranties, expressed or implied, regarding the continuous availability of the Command Center. We are not liable for any data loss, dropped connections, or errors that occur while interacting with the live stream.</p>

            <h3 style="color: var(--accent-red); margin-top: 2rem;">6. Third-Party Services</h3>
            <p>Our website utilizes third-party services including Google (for authentication), Cloudflare (for network routing), and YouTube (for live video embedding). Your use of these specific features is also subject to the respective terms of service of those platforms, including the <a href="https://www.youtube.com/t/terms" style="color: var(--accent-red); text-decoration: underline;">YouTube Terms of Service</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout>